  "text": "Instructors' goal orientation. The children's version of the Perceptions of Success Questionnaire (POSQ-CH; [CITATION_1] ) is used to quantitatively assess novice instructors' goal orientation. The questionnaire consists of 12 items (\"In physical activity, I feel most successful when … \" followed by phrases, such as \"I try hard\" and \"I do better than others\".). Ratings are based on a 5-point Likert scale (1 = strongly disagree and 5 = strongly agree). The validity and reliability of the Finnish version have been reported in [CITATION_2] .",
